ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Infrastructure and Communities as the Minister for the Purposes of the Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2021-947 of October 26, 2021; and (2) designating the Minister of INFRASTRUCTURE AND COMMUNITIES, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the CANADA MORTGAGE AND HOUSING CORPORATION ACT.
